ACTION:
Open the inspection panel of Control Module 3 (without changing any wiring), keep its switch in the ON position, and with the battery connected measure: (1) continuity of the main series path across the switch terminals; (2) voltage from its input + to input −; (3) voltage from its output + to output −; and (4) continuity directly between input + and output +, and between input − and output −. This will distinguish whether the main series conductors are open inside module 3 (independent of the switch/indicator circuit) or whether the problem is in the switch/LED branch only.
